climate change. Perhaps yours is too

No matter what your age is, climate change can be a major issue in your life. It is something that affects everyone and it can either make life fun, or make it hard for you to complete day-to-day activities. You, however, may not have noticed what climate change is or how else it is a problem in your daily life. What This Little Bangladesh Town In Medicine Hat Is Doing Will Blow Your Mind

This past summer, when the government of Alberta declared a state of emergency because of wildfires and extreme heat, a Muslim non-profit in Medicine Hat tried to do something about it. It appears to be a small, modest centre set up in a basement – initially a mosque, but later converted into a non-profit called WES Foundation. The page, however, has since been deleted.
